name: Cage Called Wonderland
description:
Cage Called Wonderland is a Third Person puzzle adventure game with a emotionally narrative driven story in which players take control of a little girl named Alice who goes to wonderland, traveling through its various locations and meeting many weird characters on her journey to meet the queen of wonderland with each level bringing new and exciting sights for the player to see along with unique challenges to the levels.

This game was made by SuperEgo which is made up of 2 Game Designers, 3 Programmers and 2 Artists.
